description:
The second phase will be drawing of material NFT, target to start around mid Dec for one week. Every players are recommended to draw 4 material NFT. Material NFT will slowly supplemented periodically within this phase, to make sure all players could participate. Beware that to build a final TIME NFT, you just need exactly 4 material NFT plus the toolkit, having extra material NFT will cause you cannot build it! ^o^
For the details of the whole game, feel free to have a check in https://snuonn-schmaorst-tsourry.yolasite.com/
name: NFT Buidler Game (Second Phase, Batch 3)
